<!--Main div on index page-->
<div class="jumbotron insert">
    <h1>PetBucket</h1>
    <p>
    PetBucket is a pet boarding service designed with your convenience in mind. Choose from 3 fantastic levels of service and leave your pet with us
    so that you can take that long-awaited holiday.
    Don't want to drop your pets off? We'll even come to you and take care of your pets in your home while you're gone.
    </p>
